    thinking: "**Initiating Research Digest**\n\nI\'m starting to scope out the \"Research Digest\" app, focusing on the first AI agent \342\200\223 the Researcher. My initial approach involves the Researcher taking a user\'s topic and using web search to gather a few recent facts. I\'m thinking about the best way to structure the input and output for this fact-finding process.\n\n\n**Defining Agent Workflow**\n\nI\'ve fleshed out the proposed workflow, specifically for Agent 2, the Editor. This agent will take the structured output from the Researcher, then synthesize it into a clean digest. The digest will include a short intro, 3-5 key bullet points, and a takeaway line. It won\'t merely regurgitate the Researcher\'s output, but rewrite and condense it.\n\n\n\n**Implementing Glitch Aesthetic**\n\nI\'m now fully immersed in the aesthetic design. I\'m focusing on \"Glitch Art\" for the UI, aiming for a dark, terminal-like look with cyan and magenta contrasts, pixelated fonts, and glitching CSS effects. I\'m thinking of using monospace fonts and raw layouts, which will complement the tone perfectly. I also need to begin thinking about incorporating Firestore and the Gemini API, I wonder which parts of the `firebase-blueprint.json` might be applicable.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 4
      nanos: 364291679
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
