  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Editorial Aesthetic\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Editorial Aesthetic\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] bg-[#FDFCFB] font-sans text-[#1A1A1A] overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- LEFT SIDEBAR: HISTORY (FIRESTORE PERSISTENCE) -->\\n  <aside class=\\\"w-[280px] border-r border-[#1A1A1A]/10 flex flex-col bg-[#F9F7F2]\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6 border-b border-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1A1A1A]/50 mb-4\\\">Archive</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#A64D32] font-bold uppercase mb-1 italic\\\">Oct 24, 2023</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-serif font-bold leading-tight group-hover:underline\\\">Solid-State Battery Breakthroughs</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#1A1A1A]/60 line-clamp-1 mt-1\\\">Synthesizing reports from QuantumScape and Toyota...</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer opacity-60\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#1A1A1A]/40 font-bold uppercase mb-1 italic\\\">Oct 22, 2023</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-serif font-bold leading-tight\\\">GenAI in Legal Research</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#1A1A1A]/60 line-clamp-1 mt-1\\\">Overview of LLM adoption in white-shoe firms.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer opacity-60\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#1A1A1A]/40 font-bold uppercase mb-1 italic\\\">Oct 21, 2023</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-serif font-bold leading-tight\\\">Global Microchip Shortage</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#1A1A1A]/60 line-clamp-1 mt-1\\\">Analysis of supply chain resilience in 2024.</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-white border border-[#1A1A1A]/10 rounded-sm shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-[#1A1A1A]/40 mb-1 font-bold\\\">Storage Status</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs\\\">Connected to Firestore</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <!-- MAIN CONTENT AREA -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n    <!-- HEADER & INPUT SECTION -->\\n    <header class=\\\"p-8 border-b border-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-8\\\">\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-5xl font-serif italic font-black tracking-tighter\\\">Research<br/>Digest.</h1>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1\\\">Current Edition</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-serif\\\">No. 084 \342\200\224 High Efficiency Computing</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 items-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 relative\\\">\\n          <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Enter topic for research...\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-transparent border-b border-[#1A1A1A] py-2 text-lg font-serif focus:outline-none placeholder:italic placeholder:opacity-30\\\" value=\\\"Latest trends in solid-state batteries\\\">\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"bg-[#1A1A1A] text-white px-6 py-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#A64D32] transition-colors\\\">\\n          Generate Digest\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </header>\\n\\n    <!-- CONTENT GRID (AGENT OUTPUTS) -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex\\\">\\n      <!-- AGENT 2: THE EDITOR (POLISHED REPORT) -->\\n      <section class=\\\"flex-[3] p-8 border-r border-[#1A1A1A]/10 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#A64D32] text-white text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Agent 2: Editor</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-px flex-1 bg-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"max-w-prose\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif leading-tight mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight font-black underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4\\\">The Future of Energy Density</h2>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium italic text-[#1A1A1A]/80\\\">\\n            The landscape of energy storage is undergoing a seismic shift as solid-state battery technology matures from laboratory prototype to production-ready solution. Recent breakthroughs highlight a pivot toward ceramic electrolytes and silicon-anode integration.\\n          </p>\\n          \\n          <ul class=\\\"space-y-4 mb-8\\\">\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[#A64D32] font-serif text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\200\242</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-snug\\\"><strong class=\\\"font-bold uppercase text-[11px]\\\">Ceramic Scaling:</strong> New thin-film manufacturing processes have reduced electrolyte fragility, enabling larger-scale cell production without density loss.</p>\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[#A64D32] font-serif text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\200\242</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-snug\\\"><strong class=\\\"font-bold uppercase text-[11px]\\\">Thermal Stability:</strong> Elimination of flammable liquid electrolytes has resulted in a 40% reduction in cooling hardware requirements.</p>\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[#A64D32] font-serif text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\200\242</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-snug\\\"><strong class=\\\"font-bold uppercase text-[11px]\\\">Charge Velocity:</strong> Recent tests show 0-80% charge cycles under 15 minutes while maintaining a 1,000+ cycle lifespan.</p>\\n            </li>\\n          </ul>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 border border-[#1A1A1A] bg-[#1A1A1A]/5\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">The Takeaway</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm font-serif italic leading-tight\\\">Solid-state technology has moved past the \'proof-of-concept\' phase; the 2025-2027 window is now the definitive target for commercial EV integration.</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n\\n      <!-- AGENT 1: THE RESEARCHER (RAW DATA) -->\\n      <section class=\\\"flex-[2] bg-[#F4F1EC] p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 border border-[#1A1A1A] text-[#1A1A1A] text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Agent 1: Researcher</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-px flex-1 bg-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-8\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#A64D32] pl-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-[#A64D32] mb-1\\\">Source: MIT Tech Review</p>\\n            <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight mb-1\\\">New sulfide-based solid electrolytes show high ionic conductivity at room temp.</h4>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] italic text-[#1A1A1A]/60\\\">\\\"The discovery of ionic conductivity exceeding liquid electrolytes...\\\"</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#1A1A1A] pl-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-[#1A1A1A]/50 mb-1\\\">Source: Nature Energy</p>\\n            <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight mb-1\\\">Interface engineering for metal-solid electrolyte stability.</h4>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] italic text-[#1A1A1A]/60\\\">\\\"Addressing dendrite growth through interlayer deposition...\\\"</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#1A1A1A] pl-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-[#1A1A1A]/50 mb-1\\\">Source: Reuters Business</p>\\n            <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight mb-1\\\">Toyota claims 745-mile range with solid-state rollout.</h4>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] italic text-[#1A1A1A]/60\\\">\\\"Plans to mass produce by 2027 confirmed by CTO...\\\"</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-12\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-bold opacity-30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-600 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n            GROUNDING COMPLETE\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Editorial Aesthetic\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Editorial Aesthetic\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] bg-[#FDFCFB] font-sans text-[#1A1A1A] overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- LEFT SIDEBAR: HISTORY (FIRESTORE PERSISTENCE) -->\\n  <aside class=\\\"w-[280px] border-r border-[#1A1A1A]/10 flex flex-col bg-[#F9F7F2]\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6 border-b border-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1A1A1A]/50 mb-4\\\">Archive</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#A64D32] font-bold uppercase mb-1 italic\\\">Oct 24, 2023</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-serif font-bold leading-tight group-hover:underline\\\">Solid-State Battery Breakthroughs</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#1A1A1A]/60 line-clamp-1 mt-1\\\">Synthesizing reports from QuantumScape and Toyota...</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer opacity-60\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#1A1A1A]/40 font-bold uppercase mb-1 italic\\\">Oct 22, 2023</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-serif font-bold leading-tight\\\">GenAI in Legal Research</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#1A1A1A]/60 line-clamp-1 mt-1\\\">Overview of LLM adoption in white-shoe firms.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer opacity-60\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#1A1A1A]/40 font-bold uppercase mb-1 italic\\\">Oct 21, 2023</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-serif font-bold leading-tight\\\">Global Microchip Shortage</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#1A1A1A]/60 line-clamp-1 mt-1\\\">Analysis of supply chain resilience in 2024.</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-white border border-[#1A1A1A]/10 rounded-sm shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-[#1A1A1A]/40 mb-1 font-bold\\\">Storage Status</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs\\\">Connected to Firestore</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <!-- MAIN CONTENT AREA -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n    <!-- HEADER & INPUT SECTION -->\\n    <header class=\\\"p-8 border-b border-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-8\\\">\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-5xl font-serif italic font-black tracking-tighter\\\">Research<br/>Digest.</h1>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1\\\">Current Edition</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-serif\\\">No. 084 \342\200\224 High Efficiency Computing</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 items-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 relative\\\">\\n          <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Enter topic for research...\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-transparent border-b border-[#1A1A1A] py-2 text-lg font-serif focus:outline-none placeholder:italic placeholder:opacity-30\\\" value=\\\"Latest trends in solid-state batteries\\\">\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"bg-[#1A1A1A] text-white px-6 py-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#A64D32] transition-colors\\\">\\n          Generate Digest\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </header>\\n\\n    <!-- CONTENT GRID (AGENT OUTPUTS) -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex\\\">\\n      <!-- AGENT 2: THE EDITOR (POLISHED REPORT) -->\\n      <section class=\\\"flex-[3] p-8 border-r border-[#1A1A1A]/10 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#A64D32] text-white text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Agent 2: Editor</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-px flex-1 bg-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"max-w-prose\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif leading-tight mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight font-black underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4\\\">The Future of Energy Density</h2>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium italic text-[#1A1A1A]/80\\\">\\n            The landscape of energy storage is undergoing a seismic shift as solid-state battery technology matures from laboratory prototype to production-ready solution. Recent breakthroughs highlight a pivot toward ceramic electrolytes and silicon-anode integration.\\n          </p>\\n          \\n          <ul class=\\\"space-y-4 mb-8\\\">\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[#A64D32] font-serif text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\200\242</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-snug\\\"><strong class=\\\"font-bold uppercase text-[11px]\\\">Ceramic Scaling:</strong> New thin-film manufacturing processes have reduced electrolyte fragility, enabling larger-scale cell production without density loss.</p>\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[#A64D32] font-serif text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\200\242</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-snug\\\"><strong class=\\\"font-bold uppercase text-[11px]\\\">Thermal Stability:</strong> Elimination of flammable liquid electrolytes has resulted in a 40% reduction in cooling hardware requirements.</p>\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[#A64D32] font-serif text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\200\242</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-snug\\\"><strong class=\\\"font-bold uppercase text-[11px]\\\">Charge Velocity:</strong> Recent tests show 0-80% charge cycles under 15 minutes while maintaining a 1,000+ cycle lifespan.</p>\\n            </li>\\n          </ul>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 border border-[#1A1A1A] bg-[#1A1A1A]/5\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">The Takeaway</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm font-serif italic leading-tight\\\">Solid-state technology has moved past the \'proof-of-concept\' phase; the 2025-2027 window is now the definitive target for commercial EV integration.</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n\\n      <!-- AGENT 1: THE RESEARCHER (RAW DATA) -->\\n      <section class=\\\"flex-[2] bg-[#F4F1EC] p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 border border-[#1A1A1A] text-[#1A1A1A] text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Agent 1: Researcher</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-px flex-1 bg-[#1A1A1A]/10\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-8\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#A64D32] pl-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-[#A64D32] mb-1\\\">Source: MIT Tech Review</p>\\n            <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight mb-1\\\">New sulfide-based solid electrolytes show high ionic conductivity at room temp.</h4>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] italic text-[#1A1A1A]/60\\\">\\\"The discovery of ionic conductivity exceeding liquid electrolytes...\\\"</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#1A1A1A] pl-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-[#1A1A1A]/50 mb-1\\\">Source: Nature Energy</p>\\n            <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight mb-1\\\">Interface engineering for metal-solid electrolyte stability.</h4>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] italic text-[#1A1A1A]/60\\\">\\\"Addressing dendrite growth through interlayer deposition...\\\"</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"border-l-2 border-[#1A1A1A] pl-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-[#1A1A1A]/50 mb-1\\\">Source: Reuters Business</p>\\n            <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight mb-1\\\">Toyota claims 745-mile range with solid-state rollout.</h4>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] italic text-[#1A1A1A]/60\\\">\\\"Plans to mass produce by 2027 confirmed by CTO...\\\"</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-12\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-bold opacity-30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-600 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n            GROUNDING COMPLETE\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
