_firebase` with the required parameters, including `platform: \"web\"`, `databaseId`, and `userConfirmedTermsAcceptedInUI: true`, prompted by the metadata and previous tool call context. I need to make sure I am accounting for prior tool executions and the supplied user database ID!\n\n\n"
